data.title: Leicester Branch Programme – Society of Recorder Players
data.text:
We meet from 2.30 – 5pm on Saturdays. Visitors are very welcome to all our meetings.

We play music from a different selection each year. Music is provided along with a folder so that you can practise at home. Please bring a music stand to meetings.

See below for a list of music for 2022- 2023
